snippet.title: C64 Game: Bongo
snippet.description:
Bongo? More like PONGO. This circus-themed game stinks. A title screen that a five-year-old could draw in an hour and a senseless running around for flashing objects while some weirdo chases you around. 

Published: 1984, Kingsoft / Anirog
Programmer: Udo Gertz

Advert: https://archive.org/details/commodore-user-magazine-31/page/n51/mode/2up
